# Career-Ops Command Center — environment

# Override the path to the career-ops repo root.
# Default: the parent directory of this web app (career-ops/web -> career-ops).
# Set this when deploying the app somewhere the data lives elsewhere.
# CAREER_OPS_ROOT=/absolute/path/to/career-ops

# Ollama server URL (local models for JD evaluation).
# Default: http://localhost:11434
# OLLAMA_HOST=http://localhost:11434

# --- Inbox (application responses) ---
# Watch your job-search mailbox for replies from companies you applied to.
# Read-only IMAP. For Gmail, create an App Password (requires 2FA):
#   https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# IMAP_USER=you@gmail.com
# IMAP_PASSWORD=your-16-char-app-password
# IMAP_HOST=imap.gmail.com   # default
# IMAP_PORT=993              # default
